            "detailed_description": "Capsule is a narrative driven escape the room game for the HTC Vive. Set in an alternate universe 1982 following a nuclear attack, Capsule requires the player to navigate lateral thinking puzzles in order to escape a fallout shelter and be rescued. The story is told indirectly through audio tapes that can be found throughout the environment. You can try to find them all, or if you rather, simply ignore them. The solutions to puzzles are randomized with each new game, so what works for one player, wouldn't work for another and each subsequent playthrough would have to be done from scratch.",
